ne with immunosuppressive or myelosuppressive agents should be avoided if possible.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/62225/', '', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Abatacept, Anakinra, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, More', 'Tetracycline, Mupirocin, Rifamycin, Oxytetracycline, Bacitracin, Demeclocycline, Rifaximin, Gentamicin, Amikacin, Neomycin, Tetracycline, More', 1767369485);
